s gratuit\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500\"/></div><div class=\"p-6 sm:p-8\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)] mb-3\"><span class=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\"><i class=\"fas fa-calendar-alt text-xs\"></i>18 mars 2026</span><span class=\"w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-text-muted)]\"></span><span class=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\"><i class=\"fas fa-clock text-xs\"></i>5 min de lecture</span></div><h2 class=\"text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold mb-2 group-hover:text-[var(--color-purple)] transition-colors duration-300\">Guide du générateur de filigranes gratuit</h2><p class=\"text-[var(--color-text-muted)] leading-relaxed\">Protégez vos photos et créations visuelles avec des filigranes efficaces. Guide complet des meilleures pratiques et outils gratuits.</p><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 mt-4 text-sm font-semibold text-[var(--color-purple)] group-hover:gap-2.5 transition-all duration-300\">Lire la suite<!-- --> <i class=\"fas fa-arrow-right text-xs\"></i></span></div></a><a class=\"glass-card overflow-hidden block hover:border-[var(--color-border-hover)] transition-all duration-300 group\" href=\"/fr/blog/tiktok-video-format-guide\"><div class=\"w-full h-48 sm:h-56 overflow-hidden\"><img src=\"/blog/tiktok-format-hero.jpg\" alt=\"Guide des formats vidéo pour TikTok\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500\"/></div><div class=\"p-6 sm:p-8\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)] mb-3\"><span class=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\"><i class=\"fas fa-calendar-alt text-xs\"></i>18 mars 2026</span><span class=\"w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-text-muted)]\"></span><span class=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\"><i class=\"fas fa-clock text-xs\"></i>5 min de lecture</span></div><h2 class=\"text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold mb-2 group-hover:text-[var(--color-purple)] transition-